      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/13794.Will_Self">About Will Self</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/13794.Will_Self"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1436638852p3/13794.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/13794.Will_Self">Will Self
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
886
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4160812538094199482">William Self is an English novelist, reviewer and columnist. He received his education at University College School, Christ&apos;s College Finchley, and Exeter College, Oxford. He was married to the late journalist Deborah Orr.<br/><br/>Self is known for his satirical, grotesque and fantastic novels and short stories set in seemingly parallel universes.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText4160812538094199482" style="display:none">William Self is an English novelist, reviewer and columnist. He received his education at University College School, Christ's College Finchley, and Exeter College, Oxford. He was married to the late journalist Deborah Orr.<br /><br />Self is known for his satirical, grotesque and fantastic novels and short stories set in seemingly parallel universes.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="4160812538094199482" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
